cabinTypes.name: Lower Deck Cabins
cabinTypes.description:
Each cabin on Argo is a distinctly themed room. All cabins include shelves, drawers and hanging hooks, a desk and chair, a luxury, private bathroom with granite counters equipped with 110-volt outlets suitable for your electronic equipment. The room has its own thermostat to control the air-conditioning and is carpeted throughout with a circular porthole. There is a satellite telephone for international calls and a flat screen TV with DVD player. 
Cabin 1 and 2 with two twin size beds are themed by hand painted artwork by Carlos Hiller 
Cabin 3 has a Whale theme with one queen size bed and optional upper twin-size bed
Cabin 4 has a Sailfish theme with two twin size beds
Cabin 5 has a Dolphin theme with one queen size bed and optional upper twin-size bed
Cabin 6 has a Turtle theme with one queen size bed and optional upper twin-size bed

cabinTypes.name: Upper Deck Cabins
cabinTypes.description:
All upper deck cabins have one queen size bed and optional upper twin-size bed.
Each cabin on Argo is a distinctly themed room. All cabins include shelves, drawers and hanging hooks, a desk and chair, a luxury, private bathroom with granite counters equipped with 110-volt outlets suitable for your electronic equipment. The room has its own thermostat to control the air-conditioning and is carpeted throughout with a large windows. There is a satellite telephone for international calls and a flat screen TV with DVD player. 
Cabin 7 has a Manta ray theme
Cabin 8 has a Sting ray theme
Cabin 9 has a Tiger shark theme

cabinTypes.name: Pala (Nutmeg)
cabinTypes.description:
The Pala cabin is large double cabin on the Main Deck level spanning almost the entire width of the boat.
The cabin is adorned with large forward facing windows and a skylight.
The Pala cabin has en-suite separate shower and bathroom.
This cabin is also equipped with an individually controlled air conditioning unit.

cabinTypes.name: Cengkeh (Clove)
cabinTypes.description:
The Cengkeh cabin is on the lower deck and can be used as either a twin cabin or a double cabin as the twin single beds have been especially designed to be joined to form a comfortable double bed.
The cabin is also equipped with an individually controlled air conditioning unit.
Natural light and natural ventilation is provided by a porthole and a large skylight.
This allows guests to switch off the individual air conditioning have have the cool sea breeze and gentle sounds of the ocean soothe them to sleep.
This cabin is serviced by an en suite combined shower and toilet.

cabinTypes.name: Pandan (Pandan)
cabinTypes.description:
This cabin can accommodate up to 3 guests on Private Charters or a maximum of 2 guests on Cabin Trips in a double and/or single bunk bed configuration. This cabin can also be used for two single guests.
This cabin is also equipped with an individual air conditioning system.
Natural light and natural ventilation is provided by a porthole and a skylight.
This allows guests to turn off the air conditioning and enjoy the cool sea breeze while the gentle sounds of the ocean soothe them to sleep.
This cabin is served by a combined shower and toilet.

cabinTypes.name: Kayu Manis (Cinnamon)
cabinTypes.description:
This cabin can accommodate up to 3 guests on Private Charters or a maximum of 2 guests on Cabin Trips in a double and/or single bunk bed configuration. This cabin can also be used for two single guests.
This cabin is also equipped with an individual air conditioning system.
Natural light and natural ventilation is provided by a porthole and a skylight.
This allows guests to turn off the air conditioning and enjoy the cool sea breeze while the gentle sounds of the ocean soothe them to sleep.
This cabin is served by a combined shower and toilet.
